  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase the Settings of RepairQ, including:</p><ul><li><p>RepairQ Account and how to modify your subscription</p></li><li><p>Integrations</p></li><li><p>Locations: store info, tax settings, location specific integrations, reset location data</p></li><li><p>Terminals (VCTs)</p></li><li><p>Announcements</p></li><li><p>Notifications (email and SMS)</p></li><li><p>Print Settings: receipts, invoices, emails, and labels</p></li><li><p>Customers: referrals, segments, contact methods</p></li><li><p>Tickets: Custom Forms, statuses, taxes, Payment Methods, Ticket Resolutions, Warranties/Disclaimers, warranty claims, and invoicing</p></li><li><p>Inventory: Item Types, Manufacturers, Catalog, Carriers, Suppliers, Shippers, conditions, statuses, and Purchase Orders</p></li><li><p>Other: image library, Validation Rules, Miscellaneous</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/2cPemjAatHw\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/2cPemjAatHw</a><p> Additionial Resources</p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1928921186/RepairQ+Subscription+Management+Change+Your+Subscription\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1928921186\" data-linked-resource-version=\"19\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RepairQ Subscription Management: Changing Your Subscription</a> </p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933410332/Setting+up+and+Assigning+Tax+Rates\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933410332\" data-linked-resource-version=\"20\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Setting up Taxes</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1928986689/Location+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1928986689\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Location Settings Overview</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246465/Automated+Notification+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933246465\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Automated Notification Resources</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361958/Print+Settings+-+Receipt+Template\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361958\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Receipts</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933377656/Print+Settings+-+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933377656\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Invoices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312070/Managing+Customer+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Managing Customer Profiles</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932394664/Assigning+a+Customer+Referral+Source\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932394664\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Assigning a Customer Referral Source</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932492983/Creating+Custom+Forms\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932492983\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating and Working with Custom Forms</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932329027/Creating+a+New+Item+Type\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932329027\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a New Item Type</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1931018355/The+RepairQ+Catalog\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1931018355\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Overview</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361894/Company+Miscellaneous+Application+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361894\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Miscellaneous Application Settings Overview</a>      </p>",
